Author: Cryptorobotics.io
Title: [ANN] CRYPTOROBOTICS.IO - trade terminal of the future
Body: Great news! Meet our changelog messages back! Today we will tell you what we have changed in our terminal over the past two months:  ⚙Connected "Multiple accounts": Now you can add an unlimited number of accounts from one exchange. This feature is available to pro-account owners in the PRO100S + package.  🔩Upgraded Smart-orders. Modified mechanics allows you to close positions on Stop Loss and Take Profit more precisely.  📝Upgraded "Alerts". When creating an alert you can specify 4 conditions for price tracking: price higher than demand, price higher than supply, price lower than demand, price lower than supply. This will allow you to receive more accurate notifications of price values.  📈In the "Orders" section, we divided all orders into different types: Limit orders, Stop limit orders, Smart orders.  📉Added the ability to manually adjust the status of the order: if you have closed orders on the exchange yourself you can change the status of the order in the terminal.  🗄Created Wiki knowledge base. In there you can find the description and step-by-step guide on all terminal features.  📍Added links to text and video instructions to make it easier for you to find the information you need in the terminal.  🤖Added Take Profit to the robot settings. Now the robot tracks the exit signal and Take Profit.  ⛓ In the robot settings currency pairs are now divided into "Recommended" and "Not Recommended" to achieve higher rates in automated trading. Now you can change some settings without stopping the robot.  📖Updated the Russian and English versions of the terminal: all pop-up notifications are displayed in the selected language.  🛠Updated terminal interface: stylized blocks and added modern animation. Now it is more convenient to work in the terminal.  💻Fixed bugs, improve terminal performance.  Follow our news to be the first to know all updates.

Author: Cryptorobotics.io
Title: [ANN] CRYPTOROBOTICS.IO - trade terminal of the future
Body: Crypto-trading is a serious thing but when it comes to professional development it is good to mix statistics with something more interesting. Here are some inspirational films about money, success and traders:  «The wolf of Wall Street». A film about the trader fraud with Leonardo DiCaprio starring, based on a real story. There is something to think about and what to learn from the main character.  «The Pursuit of Happyness». Another true story about the life of Chris Gardner, which makes you believe in luck and perseverance. Chris Gardner lost everything, lived homeless with his son, trained in trading and managed to create an entire empire.  «Limitless». Every trader at least once wanted to eat a magic pill that will make the brain work at full speed. The film says: in our life, everything is in our hands. So stop staring at the screen, go trade.  Good luck and profits!

Author: Cryptorobotics.io
Title: [ANN] CRYPTOROBOTICS.IO - trade terminal of the future
Body: Investor and writer Karl Richards came up with the definition of a “behavior gap” - when the income of an investor is much lower than the profitability of the investment itself. It is during the behavioral gap when a trader makes a radically wrong decision. They make mistakes under the influence of two strong emotions: fear and greed.  Traders buy coins at a high price because they hope for greater growth - greed. Sell at a low because they are afraid of a greater fall - fear. And it can continue until there is no money left on the deposit.  To prove that he tells about one story with his friends. The price of their shares on the stock exchange rose sharply by several positions, and they turned to Karl for advice. They wanted to buy more shares, but he dissuaded them. A few days later the stock fell sharply, and they called him again - and again he asked not to do anything. And stocks rose again.  But for Karl investors would have bought shares at a high price and sold at too low before the new increase. The best decision during such price spikes is to do nothing.    Way out?   Karl Richards offers two solutions: choose a strategy based on emotions (fear or greed) or study the market carefully before trading. Many mistakes happen just due to the lack of objective information. Traders are arrogant - they trust their inner instincts and coincidences. But in trading this approach does not work.  Understand which emotion dominates your decisions and allow the opposite one to control you. It is worth becoming a conservative and narrow the analysis tools in trading. You may miss some winning transaction but you will be aware of all the risks.  Karl also suggests constantly have an inner dialogue with yourself. Ask yourself what will happen if you hold the coins and find yourself right or false. If you hold, you earn a little more, if you make a mistake, you lose everything. This way you can precisely assess the risk.  In Cryptorobotics terminal you can connect a Pro-account with a signal channel - this way you can set more smart orders and get more profit with the help of precise signals.  Good luck!

Author: Cryptorobotics.io
Title: [ANN] CRYPTOROBOTICS.IO - trade terminal of the future
Body: We made a cool update of the terminal and added multiple accounts. Now traders can use several accounts at once from one profile and on one exchange.  How does it work: You create an account in our terminal and link all your accounts to it from one cryptocurrency exchange.  To trade, you just need to switch between accounts in one click - no need to log in again every time. You can connect an unlimited number of accounts to one account.  Also, a trader can choose the settings of smart orders for different accounts, without even switching between them.  To connect multiple accounts, you must have a Pro100S + plan. With it, you can open an unlimited number of smart orders and get access to a private signal channel. The cost for Pro100S + is $ 199 per month.  Multiaccounts is a something brand new on a crypto market. Go get to know it!  More about multiple accounts: https://golos.io/cryptorobotics/@cryptorobotics/multiple-accounts-of-cryptorobotics

Author: Cryptorobotics.io
Title: [ANN] CRYPTOROBOTICS.IO - trade terminal of the future
Body: CryptoRobotics has built a freemium cross-platform desktop trading terminal for computers (macOS and Windows), tablets and smartphones (iOS, Android, Windows mobile). Allowing you to seemingly, with one-click access, switch between major cryptocurrency exchanges. We will be carrying out a technical analysis and attempting to create trade instruments similar to those seen on traditional stock market terminals (Quik, Metatrader) and making those available to traders on our platform. We will seek to implement the following features onto the platform:  Pre-set CryptoRobots for algorithmic trading Robot Constructor Platform with an intuitive user interface for the creation and testing of trading strategies on the historical trading data Robot Marketplace selling robots created by traders in Robot Constructor Platform Trader Rankings based on trader yield curve Auto-follow Trader, allowing traders to automatically replicate successful trader transactions executed as a smart contract (Ethereum blockchain)  Furthermore, the user generated data will present another advantage – a big data advantage. Historical trades, current trades, tests, volume and variety of algorithmic trading strategies, and other interactions will p be capable of being collated, validated, integrated, enriched and then used for multiple purposes: ratings and analytics, backtesting of trading robots, and ultimately the delivery of Machine Learning and AI in CryptoRobotic trading robots. In furtherance of this goal and in setting the foundation for our platform, CryptoRobotics will be deploying a globally distributed cloud database to allow for global real-time access and low ping rate.
